Image Color Extractor

A simple web app that allows users to upload an image and extracts the top 10 most dominant colors from it. Each color is displayed with a visual preview, HEX code, and percentage, inspired by tools like Flat UI Colors.

This project combines basic image processing with NumPy and a Flask backend, along with a lightweight frontend.

Features

Upload an image from your computer

Preview the image before submission

Extract the 10 most common colors using K-Means clustering

Display each color with:

Color swatch

HEX code

Percentage occurrence

Clean and simple UI with external CSS

